<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <h1>安全、简单的用户认证系统</h1>
        <p>基于 Express + LowDB 构建的完整用户认证解决方案</p>
        
        <% if (!user) { %>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-secondary">立即注册</a>
            <a href="/login" class="btn" style="background: transparent; border: 2px solid white; color: white;">登录</a>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">进入用户中心</a>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
          <h3>安全加密</h3>
          <p>使用 bcrypt 对密码进行加密存储，保障账户安全</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📧</div>
          <h3>密码重置</h3>
          <p>支持通过邮箱链接重置密码，流程简单安全</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>快速部署</h3>
          <p>纯 JavaScript 实现，无需额外数据库配置</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
          <h3>精美界面</h3>
          <p>现代化的 UI 设计，支持响应式布局</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
